    <h4>Product Snapshot</h4>
    <p>Engage beyond your core followership. Promoted Tweets are ideal for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Sharing content and seeding interest</li>
      <li>Building awareness among relevant audiences</li>
      <li>Building a brand voice</li>
      <li>Offering deals</li>
    </ul>
    <hr />
    <h4>Get Notified</h4>
    <p>Promoted Tweets are currently in beta with a small selection of advertisers. Sign up here and get notified when Promoted Tweets launches for all advertisers.</p>
    <p><a class="btn btn-blue" href="../start">Notify me</a></p>
    <hr />
    <h4>Advertiser Analytics</h4>
    <p>Promoted Tweets come with a dedicated Promoted Tweets Dashboard, for realtime insight into your campaign's performance.</p>
